column5: BOB I did not originally mention boats at Labelles because I used my own. But if you are using the camp boats you won't find any nicer. Labelles had 17/18 Princecraft proguide boats ( wide, carpeted floors, pedestal seats, livewell, minnkota, depthfinder etc)with 40/50 4stroke Mercury. Dale also has 2 19' Princecrafts with Yamahas, one has a 4stroke 60 and the other a 2 stroke 90!! ( all tiller)
